title: Flabbergasted AS F | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 86
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
This week the babes are hella flabbergasted! Shout out Lizzo! What is the mystery behind being a twin. The babes wanna run away to a Christmas village and get lost in vibes. What's going on at the North Pole?! Sal remembers the time a person he knew wouldn't stop sneezing! What's worse than an itch you can't itch. The babes learn about a crazy twin story. Two twins lived the same life but didn't meet till late in life. What is a soul? What happens when one twin gets fat. Chris is an only child and it changed his life. Chris got rid of all his clothes and feels free. Sal is haunted by the clothes he has lost. Joe Gatto would just leave his clothes at Impractical Jokers live shows. Who has more unopened emails Chris vs Sal?!?! The babes read the first texts that were sent to their phone. HEY BABES!
